Here’s my after-work skincare routine — step by step 👇

Micellar Water: @garnierindia – removes makeup & sunscreen gently
🫧 Face Wash: @pondsindia [activated charcoal] – clears out the day’s dirt
🧴 Peeling Solution: @theordinary [AHA BHA] – gentle exfoliation for smooth, fresh skin
🫧 Cleanser: @cetaphil_india – double cleanse to make sure it’s all gone
💧 Toner: rosewater
🌿 Serum: @deconstruct_skincare [vit C] – targets [brightening/hydration]
🧴 Moisturiser: @dotandkey.skincare [hydrating gel] – locks in all the goodness,suitable for oily skin type 
💋 Lip Balm: @deconstruct_skincare [brightening lip balm ] – soft lips always and lightens pigmentation 

DM me for links to any of these products 💌
Consistency is key, and your skin will thank you 🌸
